commit 2e8b506310f6433d5558387fd568d4bfb1d6a799 upstream.

I was trying to backport the following commit to RHEL-6

    From 0cea73465cd22373c5cd43a3edd25fbd4bb532ef Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
